topics.body:
So...I've started to take commissions for fanfiction on another forum (Bell Tree). I don't get real money, but rather that forum's currency, which can be used to buy things for your Animal Crossing game, other commissions, occasionally even actual games for the 3DS. So one of my commissions is to write a story for someone's Wreck it Ralph OC who has described to me by her creator as being married to King Candy, having a high libido and sleeping with many people (her husband the most, of course!!), being very kind and caring and being to be "pretty much everything" because she is a mage. My job is to write a ship fic with her and King Candy.

Lord have mercy.
